list.name: Default
list.comment: 2.7.1 : Added img and thread packages. Redesigned cv package and created several classes like Hardware, Metric, TimeClock, Calc, Drawing, etc. Log was improved and fixed some bugs in previous version

task.summary: 2.4.4 Changed the way onInit works in Consoles
2.4.5 Bug Fix: Logs being printed on screen even when log.file is set.
2.4.5 Console: after password prompt, clear buffer and call garbage collection
2.4.6 Crypt stable. Added System.console when no mask is specified in Console
2.4.6 : Zip log files if class is present
2.4.6 : Added tests for Zip logs. Some code was further split inside Log. Added Log.enable
2.4.7 : Moved SysMain and SysService to core
2.4.9 : Added JarResource and logs should be printed when SNAPSHOT is used.
2.4.10 : Do not log stderr by default. Allow unlimited wait time in commands.
2.4.11 : WebService runs in foreground as default. Automatically detects absolute paths. Correct services path if required.
2.4.13 : Config.CfgFile added to allow any property file
2.5.0 : Config changed to allow Properties management
2.5.1 : Added 'domain' into Log to track important lines in stack
2.5.2 : Fixed visibility in logs and added color.invert
2.5.5 : Updated to Groovy 2.5.5 (groovy-extends 1.8). Fixed broken unit tests
2.5.6 : Fixed timeout in Console and exit() in SysMain
2.6: Added CV, Term and Serial Modules. Updated groovy-extend to 2.0
2.6.1: Disable colog to file by default
2.6.1: Added encoder to URL in webservice
2.6.1: Fixed log not showing correct letter (level)
2.6.2: removed new line from print in Log
2.6.4: Fixed issue in SysService not stopping properly in alternative methods. Fixed WebService on empty headers
2.6.5: Added Config default values and improved SysService stop/exit
